Megabot/Omega Boost



as there ship comes out of hyper warp towards earth there ship is in bad 
shape.


Megabot:


"Omega we got rid of the vok but are ship won't make it to the surface ."



Omega Boost:


"ok so I will transform and you can jump in."


Megabot:


"ok!"




Omega Boost transforms and Megabot jumps in. Omega blow a hole in the ship 
with his gun and they fly out and  to the earth surface then they both watch 
there ship burn up on its entery threw earth atmoshpere.


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Megabot is a blue maximals. he is only about 12. highly smart and a skilled 
fighter. his weapons are not that strong. his body is blue [and looks like 
megamans body.] he has red eyes. his beast mode is a boxer (dog).

Omega Boost is red and very big his age is 14. he isn't the that bright but 
could throw down with anyone any day. his beast mode is a squid. [he is a 
mix between omega red from x-men and Omega Boost from Omega Boost.] he could 
turn into a robot that is big enogh to fit one person inside.


Megabot and Omega Boost are best friends and always fight together. they 
came to earth to find Megabots brothers.
